data.text:
Are you looking for historic landmarks in Orlando?

The city is home to 51 historic buildings, sites, structures and objects worthy of preservation. Twelve of those are also included on the National Register of Historic Places. To nominate a site, visit our application page. You can also sign up for a guided walking tour of the Downtown Historic District.
